<br>
Group 3 (Melee centric, mixed)<br>
Arpad, 52 Shadow Knight<br>
Troyden, 51 Ranger<br>
Sheff, 51 Ranger(Group Leader)<br>
Zadrak, 50 Shadow Knight<br>
Qwen, 50 Bard<br>
Melmond, 52 Druid<br>
<br>
Group 4 (Casters, backup healers)<br>
Crafoo, 51 Magician<br>
Finlos, 52 Paladin<br>
.<br>
.<br>
.<br>
.<br>
<br>
Group 5 (Support Group. 2 Melee, and buffers).<br>
Sadili, 59 Paladin <br>
Valisbourne, 55 Cleric (Group Leader)<br>
Rothie, 56 Shaman/Druid<br>
Songbird, 56 Bard<br>
.<br>
